---
title: Chicken Katsu & Garlic Rice with Garlicky Greens & Ponzu Cucumber
description: The warm tartness with notes of sweet will pop in your mouth and it’s all thanks to this katsu sauce poured over crumbed chicken. It’s a balance of flavours, from garlicky veggies to ponzu soaked cucumber but they’re walking that tightrope with ease. It deserves a round of applause.
